articles.title: New finals structure revealed as BBL|13 schedule unveiled - cricket.com.au
articles.description: Cricket Australia unveil schedule for shortened men's Big Bash season which includes a new four-team, four-game finals structure for BBL|13
articles.content:
The top two clubs at the end of the Big Bash's regular season will retain their double-chance under a new KFC BBL finals structure confirmed today by the league.
